  _lines:
  - I'm starting to reminisce the wonderful mornings here, where I kept playing the
    celebration song to wake everyone up.
  - Yeah, I've got to say it was quite nice, but it got really annoying afterwards...
  - I know, but I still want to remember it. Could you help me find the CD while
    I pack?
  - No problem.
